movies.title: The Perks of Being a Wallflower

movies.title: Good Fortune

movies.title: Frankenstein

movies.title: Predator: Badlands
movies.description: A young Predator outcast from his clan finds an unlikely ally on his journey in search of the ultimate adversary.

movies.title: Companion

movies.title: Damsel
movies.description: A dutiful damsel agrees to marry a handsome prince, only to find the royal family has recruited her as a sacrifice to repay an ancient debt.

movies.title: Striking Rescue

movies.title: All the Devils Are Here
movies.description: Secluded in the middle of Dartmoor, Four thieves find themselves hiding out with nothing to do but count the money and time to kill.

movies.title: Mission: Impossible - The Final Reckoning
movies.description: Our lives are the sum of our choices. Tom Cruise is Ethan Hunt in Mission: Impossible - The Final Reckoning.

After 14 years in the island prison of Château d'If, he manages a daring escape. Now rich beyond his dreams, he assumes the identity of the Count of Monte-Cristo and exacts his revenge on the men who betrayed him.
movies.director: Alexandre de La Patellière, Matthieu Delaporte

movies.title: Wicked
movies.description: Elphaba, a misunderstood young woman because of her green skin, and Galinda, a popular girl, become friends at Shiz University in the Land of Oz. After an encounter with the Wonderful Wizard of Oz, their friendship reaches a crossroads.

movies.title: Nobody
movies.description: A docile family man slowly reveals his true character after his house gets burgled by two petty thieves, which, coincidentally, leads him into a bloody war with a Russian crime boss.

movies.title: Kraven the Hunter
movies.description: Kraven's complex relationship with his ruthless father, Nikolai Kravinoff, starts him down a path of vengeance with brutal consequences, motivating him to become not only the greatest hunter in the world, but also one of its most feared.

movies.title: Culpa Mía
movies.description: No synopsis available.

movies.description: In Venom: The Last Dance, Tom Hardy returns as Venom, one of Marvel's greatest and most complex characters, for the final film in the trilogy. Eddie and Venom are on the run. Hunted by both of their worlds and with the net closing in, the duo are forced into a devastating decision that will bring the curtains down on Venom and Eddie's last dance.

movies.title: Do Revenge

movies.title: The Twilight Saga: Eclipse
movies.description: As a string of mysterious killings grips Seattle, Bella, whose high school graduation is fast approaching, is forced to choose between her love for vampire Edward and her friendship with werewolf Jacob.

movies.title: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn - Part 1
movies.description: The Quileutes close in on expecting parents Edward and Bella, whose unborn child poses a threat to the Wolf Pack and the towns people of Forks.

movies.title: The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn - Part 2
movies.description: After the birth of Renesmee/Nessie, the Cullens gather other vampire clans in order to protect the child from a false allegation that puts the family in front of the Volturi.

The Protagonist will soon master the art of 'time inversion' as a way of countering the threat that is to come.

movies.description: During World War II, 855 women joined the fight to fix the three-year backlog of undelivered mail. Faced with discrimination and a country devastated by war, they managed to sort more than 17 million pieces of mail ahead of time.

movies.title: Miller's Girl
movies.description: A creative writing assignment yields complex results between a teacher and his talented student.

movies.title: Damsel
movies.description: It's the Wild West, circa 1870. Samuel Alabaster, an affluent pioneer, ventures across the American frontier to marry the love of his life, Penelope. As his group traverses the west, the once-simple journey grows treacherous, blur...

movies.description: When smart but cash-strapped teen Ellie Chu agrees to write a love letter for a jock, she doesn't expect to become his friend - or fall for his crush.

movies.title: Little Man Tate

movies.title: Buoyancy

movies.title: The Happening

movies.title: Revolutionary Road
movies.description: A young couple living in a Connecticut suburb during the mid-1950s struggle to come to terms with their personal problems while trying to raise their two children.

movies.title: I Am Legend
movies.description: Years after a plague kills most of humanity and transforms the rest into monsters, the sole survivor in New York City struggles valiantly to find a cure.

movies.title: Red One
movies.description: After Santa Claus is kidnapped, the North Pole's Head of Security must team up with a notorious hacker in a globe-trotting, action-packed mission to save Christmas.

movies.title: Wonka

movies.title: Deadpool & Wolverine
movies.description: Wolverine is recovering from his injuries when he crosses paths with the loudmouth Deadpool. They team up to defeat a common enemy.

movies.title: Constantine
movies.description: Detective Angela approaches Constantine, a demon hunter, to help her investigate her twin sister's mysterious death. As he digs deeper, he realizes that demons are trying to enter the human world.

movies.title: Hot Frosty

movies.title: Godzilla x Kong: The New Empire

movies.title: The Call of the Wild
movies.description: A sled dog struggles for survival in the wilds of the Yukon.

movies.title: The Aeronauts
movies.description: A balloon pilot and a scientist find themselves in a fight for survival while attempting to make discoveries in a gas balloon in the 1860s.

movies.description: A documentary about young women who have been drawn into the sex trade - and how easy it is for a web-savvy generation to end up making porn. The film follows several young women as they enter the amateur porn industry, exploring their motivations, experiences, and the realities of the business.

movies.title: Under Paris
movies.description: Summer 2024. Paris is hosting the World Triathlon Championships on the Seine for the first time. Sophia, a brilliant scientist, learns from Mika, a young environmental activist, that a large shark is swimming deep in the river. To avoid a bloodbath at the heart of the city, they have no choice but to join forces with Adil, the Seine river police commander.

movies.title: The Devil's Advocate
movies.description: An exceptionally adept Florida lawyer is offered a job at a high-end New York City law firm with a high-end boss - the biggest opportunity of his career to date.

movies.title: The Institute
movies.description: Subjected to bizarre, increasingly violent pseudo-scientific experiments in personality modification, brainwashing and mind control, Isabel must escape the clutches of the Rosewood Institute and exact her revenge, or else be forev...

movies.title: The Deep Web: Murdershow
movies.description: A podcaster's search for clues into his sister's death lands him on the deep web where he uncovers THE MURDERSHOW, a site where the highest crypto bidder selects how the victim will be killed. If you are watching them, they are watching you.

movies.title: A Few Good Men
movies.description: Military lawyer Lieutenant Daniel Kaffee defends Marines accused of murder. They contend they were acting under orders.

movies.title: Kleks Academy
movies.description: Teenage girl Ada ends up in mysterious Kleks Academy where crossing to the world of fairy tales and reaching boundaries of imagination is possible. She also discovers a way to find out her most hidden family secret.

movies.title: Dune: Part Two
movies.description: Paul Atreides unites with Chani and the Fremen while seeking revenge against the conspirators who destroyed his family.

movies.title: The Casagrandes Movie

movies.description: Tennis player turned coach Tashi has taken her husband, Art, and transformed him into a world-famous Grand Slam champion. To jolt him out of his recent losing streak, she signs him up for a 'Challenger' event—close to the lowest level of pro tournament—where he finds himself standing across the net from his former best friend and Tashi's former boyfriend.

movies.title: The Menu
movies.description: A young couple travels to a remote island to eat at an exclusive restaurant where the chef has prepared a lavish menu, with some shocking surprises.

movies.title: Are You There God? It's Me, Margaret.
movies.description: When her family moves from the city to the suburbs, 11-year-old Margaret navigates new friends, feelings, and the beginning of adolescence.

movies.title: You Are So Not Invited to My Bat Mitzvah

movies.title: Venom: Let There Be Carnage
movies.description: Eddie Brock struggles to adjust to his new life as the host of the alien symbiote Venom, which grants him super-human abilities in order to be a lethal vigilante. Brock attempts to reignite his career by interviewing serial killer Cletus Kasady, who becomes the host of the symbiote Carnage and escapes prison after a failed execution.

movies.title: Uncharted
movies.description: Street-smart Nathan Drake is recruited by seasoned treasure hunter Victor 'Sully' Sullivan to recover a fortune amassed by Ferdinand Magellan, and lost 500 years ago by the House of Moncada.

movies.title: Jungle Cruise
movies.description: Dr. Lily Houghton enlists the aid of wisecracking skipper Frank Wolff to take her down the Amazon in his dilapidated boat. Together, they search for an ancient tree that holds the power to heal – a discovery that will change the future of medicine.

movies.title: The Marvels
movies.description: Carol Danvers gets her powers entangled with those of Kamala Khan and Monica Rambeau, forcing them to work together to save the universe.

movies.title: The Deepest Breath
movies.description: A champion freediver and expert safety diver seemed destined for one another despite the different paths they took to meet at the pinnacle of the freediving world. A look at the thrilling rewards — and inescapable risks — of chasing dreams through the depths of the ocean.

movies.title: Inception
movies.description: A thief who enters the dreams of others to steal secrets from their subconscious is given a chance to have his criminal history erased as payment for the implantation of another person's idea into a target's subconscious.

movies.title: King Kong
movies.description: In 1933 New York, an overly ambitious movie producer coerces his cast and hired ship crew to travel to mysterious Skull Island, where they encounter Kong, a giant ape who is immediately smitten with the leading lady.

movies.title: The Day After Tomorrow
movies.description: Jack Hall, a paleoclimatologist, must make a daring trek from Washington, D.C. to New York City to reach his son, trapped in the crosshairs of a sudden international storm which plunges the planet into a new Ice Age.

movies.title: Ant-Man
movies.description: Armed with the astonishing ability to shrink in scale but increase in strength, master thief Scott Lang must embrace his inner-hero and help his mentor, Doctor Hank Pym, protect the secret behind his spectacular Ant-Man suit from a new generation of towering threats.

movies.title: Wonder Woman
movies.description: When an American pilot crashes on the shores of her sheltered island paradise and tells tales of a massive conflict raging in the outside world, Diana leaves her home, convinced she can stop the threat. Fighting alongside man in a war to end all wars, Diana will discover her full powers... and her true destiny.

movies.title: Killers of the Flower Moon
movies.description: Members of the Osage tribe in the United States are murdered under mysterious circumstances in the 1920s, sparking a major FBI investigation involving J. Edgar Hoover.

movies.title: Sweet Karma
movies.description: A mute Russian girl infiltrates Toronto's underground sex trade to avenge the death of her sister.

movies.title: Ballerina
movies.description: Grieving the loss of a best friend she couldn't protect, an ex-bodyguard sets out to fulfill her dear friend's last wish: sweet revenge.

movies.title: Royalteen – Princess Margrethe
movies.description: Princess Margrethe deals with the aftermath of last year's prom drama, family secrets, and a budding romance with a Danish prince as the royal families of Norway and Denmark come together.

movies.title: Kiss Kiss Bang Bang
movies.description: A murder mystery brings together a private eye, a struggling actress, and a thief masquerading as an actor. As they unravel the case, they find themselves entangled in a web of lies, deception, and Hollywood satire.

movies.title: Through My Window: Across the Sea
movies.description: After a year apart, Raquel and Ares reunite for a summer on the Spanish coast, but their relationship is tested by jealousy, secrets, and new temptations.

movies.title: Heart of Stone
movies.description: An intelligence operative for a shadowy global peacekeeping agency races to stop a hacker from stealing its most valuable and dangerous weapon.

movies.title: Ammonite
movies.description: In 1840s England, palaeontologist Mary Anning and a young woman sent by her husband to convalesce by the sea develop an intense relationship that changes both their lives.

movies.title: The Super Mario Bros. Movie

movies.title: Antman And The Wasp Quantumania
movies.description: Super-Hero partners Scott Lang and Hope van Dyne, along with Hope's parents Janet van Dyne and Hank Pym, and Scott's daughter Cassie Lang, find themselves exploring the Quantum Realm, interacting with strange new creatures and embarking on an adventure that will push them beyond the limits of what they thought possible.

movies.title: The Usual Suspects
movies.description: The sole survivor of a pier shoot-out tells the story of how a notorious criminal influenced the events that began with five criminals meeting in a seemingly random police lineup.

movies.title: War Dogs
movies.description: Loosely based on the true story of two young men, David Packouz and Efraim Diveroli, who won a three hundred million dollar contract from the Pentagon to arm America's allies in Afghanistan.

movies.title: Guardians of the Galaxy Volume 3
movies.description: Peter Quill, still reeling from the loss of Gamora, must rally his team around him to defend the universe along with protecting one of their own. A mission that, if not completed successfully, could quite possibly lead to the end of the Guardians as we know them.

movies.title: Air
movies.description: Discover the game-changing partnership between a then undiscovered Michael Jordan and Nike's fledgling basketball division which revolutionized the world of sports and culture with the Air Jordan brand.

movies.title: Fast X
movies.description: Over many missions and against impossible odds, Dom Toretto and his family have outsmarted, out-nerved and outdriven every foe in their path. Now, they confront the most lethal opponent they've ever faced: A terrifying threat emerging from the shadows of the past who's fueled by blood revenge, and who is determined to shatter this family and destroy everything—and everyone—that Dom loves, forever.

movies.title: Oppenheimer
movies.description: The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer's role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.

movies.title: Mission: Impossible
movies.description: An American agent, under false suspicion of disloyalty, must discover and expose the real spy without the help of his organization.

movies.title: Mission: Impossible II
movies.description: IMF agent Ethan Hunt is sent to Sydney to find and destroy a genetically modified disease called "Chimera".

movies.title: Mission: Impossible III
movies.description: IMF agent Ethan Hunt comes into conflict with a dangerous and sadistic arms dealer who threatens his life and his fiancée in response.

movies.title: Mission: Impossible - Ghost Protocol
movies.description: The IMF is shut down when it's implicated in the bombing of the Kremlin, causing Ethan Hunt and his new team to go rogue to clear their organization's name.

movies.title: Mission: Impossible - Rogue Nation
movies.description: Ethan and his team take on their most impossible mission yet when they have to eradicate an international rogue organization as highly skilled as they are and committed to destroying the IMF.

movies.title: Mission: Impossible - Fallout
movies.description: A group of terrorists plans to detonate three plutonium cores for a simultaneous nuclear attack on different cities. Ethan Hunt, along with his IMF team, sets out to stop the carnage.

movies.title: Mission: Impossible – Dead Reckoning Part One
movies.description: Ethan Hunt and his IMF team embark on their most dangerous mission yet: To track down a terrifying new weapon that threatens all of humanity before it falls into the wrong hands.

movies.title: Extraction 2

movies.title: Spider-Man 2

movies.title: Spider-Man 3

movies.title: The Amazing Spider-Man

movies.title: The Amazing Spider-Man 2

movies.title: Spider-Man: Homecoming

movies.title: Spider-Man: Far from Home

movies.title: Spider-Man: No Way Home
movies.description: With Spider-Man's identity now revealed, Peter asks Doctor Strange for help. When a spell goes wrong, dangerous foes from other worlds start to appear.

movies.title: Spider-Man: Across the Spider-Verse
movies.description: Miles Morales catapults across the Multiverse, where he encounters a team of Spider-People charged with protecting its very existence. When the heroes clash on how to handle a new threat, Miles must redefine what it means to be a hero.
movies.director: Joaquim Dos Santos, Kemp Powers, Justin K. Thompson

movies.title: Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse
movies.director: Bob Persichetti, Peter Ramsey, Rodney Rothman

movies.title: Barbie
movies.description: Barbie and Ken are having the time of their lives in the colorful and seemingly perfect world of Barbie Land. However, when they get a chance to go to the real world, they soon discover the joys and perils of living among humans.

movies.title: Journey to the Center of the Earth
movies.description: On a quest to find out what happened to his missing brother, a scientist, his nephew and their mountain guide discover a fantastic and dangerous lost world in the center of the earth.

movies.title: Escape Room: Tournament of Champions

movies.title: Escape Room: Tournament of Champions Alternate Cut

Amanda Harper (Deborah Ann Woll) and the Therapist (Lucy Newman-Williams) are only present in the Theatrical Cut. The Extended Cut introduces Isabelle Fuhrman and James Frain as Claire and Henry the puzzlemaker, respectively, along with the Tanya van Graan's uncredited appearance as Sonya, Henry's wife and Claire's mother.

movies.title: The Meg
movies.description: A deep-sea submersible -- part of an international undersea observation program -- has been attacked by a massive creature, previously thought to be extinct, and now lies disabled at the bottom of the deepest trench in the Pacific ... with its crew trapped inside. With time running out, expert deep sea rescue diver Jonas Taylor is recruited to save the crew -- and the ocean itself -- from this unstoppable threat: a pre-historic 75-foot-long shark known as the Megalodon.

movies.title: Old School
movies.description: Three friends attempt to recapture their glory days by opening up a fraternity near their alma mater.

movies.title: Shutter Island

movies.title: The Lighthouse
movies.description: Two lighthouse keepers try to maintain their sanity while living on a remote and mysterious New England island in the 1890s.

movies.title: Civil War
movies.description: In a dystopian future, four journalists travel across the United States during a nation-wide conflict. While trying to survive, they aim to reach the White House to interview the president before he is overthrown.

movies.title: A Family Affair
movies.description: An unexpected romance triggers comic consequences for a young woman, her mother, and her boss, grappling with the complications of love, sex, and identity.

movies.title: Deadpool
movies.description: A wisecracking mercenary gets experimented on and becomes immortal yet hideously scarred, and sets out to track down the man who ruined his looks.

movies.title: Deadpool 2
movies.description: Foul-mouthed mutant mercenary Wade Wilson (a.k.a. Deadpool) assembles a team of fellow mutant rogues to protect a young boy with abilities from the brutal, time-traveling cyborg Cable.

movies.title: Dead Poets Society
movies.description: Maverick teacher John Keating returns in 1959 to the prestigious New England boys' boarding school where he was once a star student, using poetry to embolden his pupils to new heights of self-expression.

movies.title: Palm Springs
movies.description: Stuck in a time loop, two wedding guests develop a budding romance while living the same day over and over again.

movies.title: How to Lose a Guy in 10 Days
movies.description: An advertising executive and ladies' man, to win a big campaign, bets that he can make a woman fall in love with him in 10 days. Meanwhile, a magazine writer is assigned to write an article on how to lose a guy in 10 days, and the two cross paths with hidden agendas.

movies.title: Irreversible
movies.description: Events over the course of one traumatic night in Paris unfold in reverse-chronological order as the beautiful Alex is brutally raped and beaten by a stranger in an underpass tunnel. Her boyfriend and ex-lover take matters into their own hands by hiring two criminals to help them find the rapist so that they can exact revenge. A simultaneously beautiful and terrible examination of the destructive nature of cause and effect, and how time destroys everything.

movies.title: Rush Hour
movies.description: A loyal and dedicated Hong Kong Inspector teams up with a reckless and loudmouthed L.A.P.D. detective to rescue the Chinese Consul's kidnapped daughter, while trying to arrest a dangerous crime lord along the way.

movies.title: Rush Hour 2
movies.description: It's vacation time for Det. James Carter and he finds himself alongside Det. Lee in Hong Kong wishing for more excitement. While Carter wants to party and meet the ladies, Lee is out to track down a Triad gang lord who may be responsible for killing two men at the American Embassy. Things get complicated as the pair stumble onto a counterfeiting plot by L.A. crime boss Steven Reign and Triad Ricky Tan, an ex-cop who played a mysterious part in the death of Det. Lee's father.

movies.title: Rush Hour 3
movies.description: After an attempted assassination on Ambassador Han, Lee and Carter head to Paris to protect a French woman with knowledge of the Triads' secret leaders.

movies.title: Luckiest Girl Alive
movies.description: A sharp-tongued New Yorker appears to have it all: a sought-after position at a glossy magazine, a killer wardrobe, and a dream Nantucket wedding on the horizon. But when the director of a crime documentary invites her to tell her side of the shocking incident that took place when she was a teenager at the prestigious Brentley School, Ani is forced to confront a dark truth that threatens to unravel her meticulously crafted life.

movies.title: The Truman Show
movies.description: An insurance salesman begins to suspect that his whole life is actually some sort of reality TV show. Truman Burbank, unaware that his entire life is being broadcast to the world, starts to notice strange occurrences and sets out to discover the truth about his existence.

movies.title: Percy Jackson & the Olympians: The Lightning Thief
movies.description: A teenager discovers he's the descendant of a Greek god and sets out on an adventure to settle an on-going battle between the gods.

movies.title: Percy Jackson: Sea of Monsters
movies.description: In order to restore their dying safe haven, the son of Poseidon and his friends embark on a quest to the Sea of Monsters, to find the mythical Golden Fleece, all the while trying to stop an ancient evil from rising.

movies.title: Sleepover
movies.description: On the last day of 8th grade before their freshman year in high school, Julie has a slumber party with three best friends. To win the legendary high-school lunch spot by the fountain, they must win an all-night scavenger hunt against their popular-girl rivals.

movies.title: The Sleepover
movies.description: When two siblings discover their seemingly normal mom is a former thief in witness protection who has been forced to pull one last job, they team up to rescue her over the course of an action-packed night.

movies.title: Stuart Little
movies.description: When the Littles adopt Stuart, the mouse, George is initially unwelcoming to his new brother, the family cat, Snowbell, is even less enthusiastic. Stuart resolves to face these difficulties with as much pluck and courage as he can...

movies.title: Stuart Little 2
movies.description: Stuart and Snowbell set out across town to rescue a friend.

movies.title: Stuart Little 3: Call of the Wild
movies.description: The Little family spend their vacation near Lake Garland. Meanwhile, in the forest, a beast is threatening the animals to give her food every night.

movies.title: Sleeping Dogs
movies.description: An ex-homicide detective with memory loss is forced to solve a brutal murder, only to uncover chilling secrets from his forgotten past.

movies.title: Me, Myself & Irene
movies.description: A nice-guy cop with Dissociative Identity Disorder must protect a woman on the run from a corrupt ex-boyfriend and his associates.

movies.title: One Eyed Girl
movies.description: A young psychiatrist is haunted by the suicide of a patient and hovers on the verge of a breakdown. He meets an attractive representative of a secret church that promises salvation to its members.

movies.title: Rain Man
movies.description: After a selfish L.A. yuppie learns his estranged father left a fortune to an autistic-savant brother in Ohio that he didn't know existed, he absconds with his brother and sets out across the country, hoping to gain a larger inheritance.

movies.title: Zathura: A Space Adventure
movies.description: Two young brothers are drawn into an intergalactic adventure when their house is hurled through the depths of space by the magical board game they are playing.

movies.title: The Chronicles of Narnia: The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe
movies.description: While playing, Lucy and her siblings find a wardrobe that lands them in a mystical place called Narnia. Here they realize that it was fated and they must now unite with Aslan to defeat an evil queen.

movies.title: The Chronicles of Narnia: Prince Caspian
movies.description: The Pevensie siblings return to Narnia, where they are enlisted to once again help ward off an evil king and restore the rightful heir to the land's throne, Prince Caspian.

movies.title: The Chronicles of Narnia: The Voyage of the Dawn Treader
movies.description: Lucy and Edmund Pevensie return to Narnia with their cousin Eustace where they meet up with Prince Caspian for a trip across the sea aboard the royal ship The Dawn Treader. Along the way they encounter dragons, dwarves, merfolk, and a band of lost warriors before reaching the edge of the world.

movies.title: Baby Driver
movies.description: A talented, young getaway driver relies on the beat of his personal soundtrack to be the best in the game. After meeting the girl of his dreams, he sees a chance to ditch his criminal life and make a clean getaway. But after being coerced into working for a crime boss, he must face the music when a doomed heist threatens his life, love and freedom.

movies.title: Alice in Wonderland
movies.description: Nineteen-year-old Alice returns to the magical world from her childhood adventure, where she reunites with her old friends and learns of her true destiny: to end the Red Queen's reign of terror.

movies.title: Alice Through the Looking Glass
movies.description: Alice returns to the magical world of Underland, only to find the Hatter in a horrible state. With the help of her friends, Alice must travel through time to save the Mad Hatter and Underland's fate from the evil clutches of the Red Queen and a clock-like creature, known as Time.

movies.title: Aladdin
movies.description: A kind-hearted street urchin vies for the love of beautiful Princess Jasmine of Agrabah. When he finds a magic lamp, he uses the genie's magic power to make himself a prince in order to marry her. He's also on a mission to stop the powerful Jafar, who plots to steal the magic lamp that could make his deepest wishes come true.

movies.title: Jumanji: Welcome to the Jungle
movies.description: Four teenagers are sucked into a magical video game, and the only way they can escape is to work together to finish the game. To beat the game and return to the real world, they must go on the most dangerous adventure of their lives, discover what Alex Vreeke left 20 years ago, and change the way they think about themselves -- or they'll be stuck in the game forever, to be played by others without break.

movies.title: Jumanji: The Next Level
movies.description: The gang is back but the game has changed. As they return to Jumanji to rescue one of their own, they discover that nothing is as they expect. The players will have to brave parts unknown and unexplored, from the arid deserts to the snowy mountains, in order to escape the world's most dangerous game.

movies.title: The Maze Runner
movies.description: Thomas is deposited in a community of boys after his memory is erased, soon learning they're all trapped in a maze that will require him to join forces with fellow "runners" for a shot at escape.

movies.title: Maze Runner: The Scorch Trials
movies.description: After having escaped the Maze, the Gladers now face a new set of challenges on the open roads of a desolate landscape filled with unimaginable obstacles.

movies.title: Maze Runner: The Death Cure
movies.description: Young hero Thomas embarks on a mission to find a cure for a deadly disease known as "The Flare".

movies.title: Pirates of the Caribbean: The Curse of the Black Pearl
movies.description: Blacksmith Will Turner teams up with eccentric pirate "Captain" Jack Sparrow to save Elizabeth Swann, the governor's daughter and his love, from Jack's former pirate allies, who are now undead.

movies.title: Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Man's Chest
movies.description: Jack Sparrow races to recover the heart of Davy Jones to avoid enslaving his soul to Jones' service, as other friends and foes seek the heart for their own agenda as well.

movies.title: Pirates of the Caribbean: At World's End
movies.description: Will Turner, Elizabeth Swann, Hector Barbossa, and the crew of the Black Pearl try and rescue Jack from davy jones locker and prepare to fight Lord Cutler Beckett, who controls Davy Jones and the Flying Dutchman.

movies.title: Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides
movies.description: Jack Sparrow and Barbossa embark on a quest to find the elusive fountain of youth, only to discover that Blackbeard and his daughter are after it too.

movies.title: Pirates of the Caribbean: Dead Men Tell No Tales
movies.description: Captain Jack Sparrow searches for the Trident of Poseidon to rule the sea while being pursued by old rival Captain Salazar and a crew of deadly ghosts who have escaped from the Devil's Triangle.

movies.title: Source Code
movies.description: A soldier wakes up in someone else's body and discovers he's part of an experimental government program to find the bomber of a commuter train within 8 minutes.

movies.title: Goosebumps
movies.description: A teen is glum about moving to a small town until he falls for his new neighbor. But her dad is a horror writer whose scary world soon turns real. When Zach accidentally unleashes the monsters from the fantastic tales, it's up to Stine, his daughter and Cooper to return the beasts back to the books where they belong.

movies.title: Goosebumps 2: Haunted Halloween
movies.description: While collecting junk one day, best friends Sonny and Sam meet Slappy, a mischievous talking dummy from an unpublished 'Goosebumps' book by R.L. Stine. Hoping to start his own family, Slappy kidnaps Sonny's mother and brings all of his ghoulish friends back to life -- just in time for Halloween. As the sleepy town becomes overrun with monsters, witches and other mysterious creatures, Sonny joins forces with his sister, Sam and a kindly neighbor to save Sonny's mom and foil Slappy's plan.

movies.title: Sherlock Holmes
movies.description: Detective Sherlock Holmes and his stalwart partner Watson engage in a battle of wits and brawn with a nemesis whose plot is a threat to all of England. When a string of brutal murders terrorizes London, it doesn't take long for legendary detective Sherlock Holmes and his crime-solving partner, Dr. Watson, to find the killer, Lord Blackwood. A devotee of the dark arts, Blackwood has a bigger scheme in mind, and his execution plays right into his plans.

movies.title: Sherlock Holmes: A Game of Shadows
movies.description: Sherlock Holmes and Dr. Watson join forces to outwit and bring down their fiercest adversary, Professor Moriarty.

movies.title: Poison Ivy
movies.description: A seductive teen befriends an introverted high school student and gradually insinuates herself into the girl's family, with disastrous results.

movies.title: Poison Ivy II: Lily
movies.description: Lily, a sheltered art student, finds a box of items belonging to a mysterious girl named Ivy and is inspired to change her life, leading to a series of dangerous liaisons.

movies.title: Poison Ivy: The New Seduction
movies.description: Violet, the sister of Ivy, returns to the Greer residence and uses her seductive powers to manipulate and destroy the family, leading to a series of deadly events. A direct-to-video erotic thriller and the third installment in the Poison Ivy series.

movies.title: Girls After Dark : Clyde Cooper
movies.description: A private investigator is hired to track down a missing girl on the run from a mysterious Silicon Valley corporation.

movies.title: Attack on Titan Part 1
movies.description: In a world where giant humanoid Titans prey on humans, Eren joins the scouting legion to get revenge on the monsters who killed everyone in his town. A live-action adaptation of the popular manga and anime series.

movies.title: Restore Point
movies.description: In 2041, humanity can cheat death by restoring people from backups after unnatural deaths. Detective Em investigates a murder case where the restoration process is sabotaged, leading to a conspiracy that questions the ethics of technological progress.

movies.title: Enola Holmes
movies.description: Enola Holmes, the teenage sister of Sherlock Holmes, sets out to find her missing mother, becoming a super-sleuth in her own right as she unravels a conspiracy that threatens the course of history.

movies.title: Enola Holmes 2
movies.description: Now a detective-for-hire, Enola Holmes takes on her first official case to find a missing girl, uncovering a dangerous conspiracy that requires the help of friends—and Sherlock himself—to unravel.

movies.title: Cinderella
movies.description: A young woman with a kind heart and a pure spirit overcomes adversity and finds love with the help of her fairy godmother. Disney's live-action adaptation of the classic fairy tale, directed by Kenneth Branagh.

movies.title: Beauty and the Beast
movies.description: A bankrupt merchant stumbles upon the enchanted castle of a hideous creature. His compassionate daughter, Belle, takes his place as the Beast's prisoner. As repugnance gradually turns into affection, only true love can break the spell.

movies.title: Beauty and the Beast
movies.description: A brave, beautiful, and brilliant young woman is imprisoned by a beast in his castle. Despite her fears, she learns to see beyond the beast's hideous exterior and realize the gentle heart of the true prince within him.

movies.title: Beauty and the Beast
movies.description: A prince cursed to spend his days as a hideous monster sets out to regain his humanity by earning a young woman's love.

movies.title: The Blind Side
movies.description: The story of Michael Oher, a homeless and traumatized boy who became an All-American football player and first-round NFL draft pick with the help of a caring woman and her family.

movies.title: Coco
movies.description: Despite his family's generations-old ban on music, young Miguel dreams of becoming an accomplished musician like his idol Ernesto de la Cruz. Desperate to prove his talent, Miguel finds himself in the stunning and colorful Land of the Dead following a mysterious chain of events. Along the way, he meets charming trickster Hector, and together, they set off on an extraordinary journey to unlock the real story behind Miguel's family history.

movies.title: Ocean's Eleven
movies.description: Danny Ocean, a recently paroled con artist, assembles a team of eleven specialists to pull off an elaborate heist targeting the vault of three Las Vegas casinos owned by ruthless mogul Terry Benedict. Their plan is to get in and out with $150 million during a major boxing event, but personal motives and high security make the job even more challenging.

movies.title: Ocean's Twelve
movies.description: Three years after their Vegas heist, Danny Ocean and his crew are forced to repay casino owner Terry Benedict. To raise the money, they head to Europe for a series of high-stakes heists, only to find themselves competing with a master thief known as the Night Fox.

movies.title: Ocean's Thirteen
movies.description: Danny Ocean and his crew reunite for a third heist after casino owner Willy Bank double-crosses one of their own. Their plan: sabotage the grand opening of Bank's new Las Vegas casino and pull off a daring revenge job.

movies.title: Ocean's Eight
movies.description: Debbie Ocean, the sister of Danny Ocean, assembles an all-female crew to pull off an impossible heist at New York City's annual Met Gala, targeting a $150 million diamond necklace.

movies.title: I Am Sam
movies.description: Sam Dawson, a man with an intellectual disability, fights for custody of his 7-year-old daughter Lucy, teaching his high-powered lawyer the value of love and family along the way.

movies.title: The Parent Trap
movies.description: Identical twins Annie and Hallie, separated at birth and each raised by one of their biological parents, discover each other for the first time at summer camp and make a plan to bring their wayward parents back together.

movies.title: The Boy in the Striped Pajamas
movies.description: During World War II, 8-year-old Bruno and his family leave Berlin to take up residence near the concentration camp where his father has just become commandant. Unhappy and lonely, he befriends Shmuel, a Jewish boy of his age, through the barbed-wire fence of the camp.

movies.title: The Curious Case of Benjamin Button
movies.description: Benjamin Button, born under unusual circumstances, ages in reverse and experiences love, loss, and the passage of time in a unique way, living his life backwards from old age to infancy.

movies.title: The Pursuit of Happyness
movies.description: A struggling salesman takes custody of his son as he's poised to begin a life-changing professional career. Based on the true story of Chris Gardner's pursuit of a better life for himself and his son.

movies.title: The Great Gatsby
movies.description: A Midwestern war veteran finds himself drawn to the past and lifestyle of his millionaire neighbor, Jay Gatsby, amid the lavish parties and drama of the Jazz Age.

movies.title: The Departed
movies.description: An undercover cop and a mole in the police attempt to identify each other while infiltrating an Irish gang in South Boston. As both organizations realize they have a mole, Billy and Colin must figure out each other's identities to save their own lives.

movies.title: Mad Max: Fury Road
movies.description: In a post-apocalyptic wasteland, Max teams up with Furiosa to escape a tyrannical ruler and help a group of women find freedom. Together, they embark on a high-speed chase across the desert, facing relentless enemies and forging an unlikely alliance.

movies.title: The Grand Budapest Hotel
movies.description: The adventures of Gustave H, a legendary concierge at a famous European hotel between the wars, and Zero Moustafa, the lobby boy who becomes his most trusted friend. The story involves the theft and recovery of a priceless Renaissance painting and the battle for an enormous family fortune.

movies.title: 2001: A Space Odyssey
movies.description: A mysterious artifact is discovered on the moon, leading humanity on a quest to Jupiter with the sentient computer HAL 9000. The journey explores themes of evolution, artificial intelligence, and the unknown, culminating in a mind-bending odyssey through space and time.

movies.title: Blade Runner 2049
movies.description: Young Blade Runner K's discovery of a long-buried secret leads him to track down former Blade Runner Rick Deckard, who's been missing for thirty years. The search uncovers hidden truths about their world and what it means to be human.

movies.title: The Shape of Water
movies.description: At a top secret research facility in the 1960s, a lonely janitor forms a unique relationship with an amphibious creature that is being held in captivity. Elisa, a mute woman, finds herself drawn to the creature and, with the help of her friends, risks everything to save him from certain death.

movies.title: Prisoners
movies.description: A desperate father takes the law into his own hands after police fail to find two kidnapped girls.

movies.title: Phantom Thread
movies.description: Set in 1950s London, renowned dressmaker Reynolds Woodcock's fastidious life is disrupted by a young, strong-willed woman, Alma, who becomes his muse and lover. Their relationship transforms both their lives in unexpected ways.

movies.title: Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood
movies.description: A faded television actor and his stunt double strive to achieve fame and success in the final years of Hollywood's Golden Age in 1969 Los Angeles. Their lives become intertwined with the infamous Manson Family.

movies.title: Pulp Fiction
movies.description: The lives of two mob hitmen, a boxer, a gangster and his wife, and a pair of diner bandits intertwine in four tales of violence and redemption in Quentin Tarantino's iconic crime drama.

movies.title: Cold Pursuit
movies.description: A snowplow driver seeks revenge against the drug dealers he thinks killed his son. His quest for justice turns into a vengeful hunt, igniting a turf war between a drug lord and a rival gang.

movies.title: Casper
movies.description: An afterlife therapist and his daughter meet a friendly young ghost when they move into a crumbling mansion in order to rid the premises of wicked spirits. Casper, the ghost of a young boy, befriends Kat and her father, but not so friendly are Casper's uncles Stretch, Fatso, and Stinkie, who are determined to drive all 'fleshies' away.

movies.title: She's Out of My League
movies.description: An average Joe meets the perfect woman, but his lack of confidence and the influence of his friends and family begin to pick away at the relationship. Kirk, a TSA agent, can't believe his luck when a gorgeous, successful woman named Molly falls in love with him.

movies.title: Death Race
movies.description: Ex-con Jensen Ames is forced by the warden of a notorious prison to compete in a car race in which inmates must brutalize and kill one another on the road to victory. To win his freedom, he must survive the deadly Death Race.

movies.title: Death Race 2
movies.description: In the near future, the United States economy declines and violent crime spirals out of control. Convicted cop-killer Carl Lucas is sent to Terminal Island, where he must compete in a deadly televised competition called Death Race to earn his freedom.

movies.title: Death Race 3: Inferno
movies.description: Convicted cop-killer Carl Lucas, aka Frankenstein, is a superstar driver in the brutal prison yard demolition derby known as Death Race. Only one victory away from winning freedom for himself and his pit crew, Lucas is plunged into an all-new competition in South Africa's Kalahari Desert.

movies.title: Knowing
movies.description: In 1959, a time capsule is buried with a cryptic message. Fifty years later, an astrophysicist discovers the message predicts disasters, and races to prevent the final catastrophe as his son becomes involved in the mystery.

movies.title: Rose Island
movies.description: In 1968, engineer Giorgio Rosa builds a platform off the Italian coast and declares it a nation, drawing the world's attention and the ire of the Italian government. Based on a true story.

movies.title: The Bad Seed Returns
movies.description: After the murderous events that left her father dead, 15-year-old Emma, a seemingly typical teenaged girl, is now living with her aunt and navigating high school. But the darkness can only be hidden for so long, especially when a new girl at school seems to know Emma's secrets.

movies.title: Private Lessons
movies.description: A teenage boy is seduced by his housemaid, who is part of a blackmail plot orchestrated by the family chauffeur. Troubles arise when the two start to fall in love.

movies.title: My Sister's Keeper
movies.description: Anna Fitzgerald, conceived as a genetic match to save her older sister Kate from leukemia, sues her parents for medical emancipation when asked to donate a kidney, fracturing the family bond. Based on the novel by Jodi Picoult.

movies.title: What Jennifer Did (2024)
movies.description: A chilling true-crime documentary about Jennifer Pan, who orchestrated a murder-for-hire plot against her parents, resulting in her mother's death and her father's severe injury. The film explores the investigation, the complex family dynamics, and the shocking twists of the case.

movies.title: A Day and a Half (2023)
movies.description: In a desperate bid to reunite with his daughter, an armed man bursts into the medical center where his estranged wife works and kidnaps her, leading to a tense road trip across rural Sweden.

movies.title: Triangle of Sadness (2022)
movies.description: A fashion model celebrity couple join a luxury cruise for the super-rich, but disaster strikes, leaving the survivors stranded on a desert island and turning the social hierarchy upside down.

movies.title: Red Notice (2021)
movies.description: An Interpol agent successfully tracks down the world's most wanted art thief with help from a rival thief. But nothing is as it seems as a series of double-crosses ensues.

movies.title: Anyone But You
movies.description: After an amazing first date, Bea and Ben's fiery attraction turns ice-cold--until they find themselves unexpectedly reunited at a wedding in Australia. So they do what any two mature adults would do: pretend to be a couple.

movies.title: Greenland
movies.description: A family fights for survival as a planet-killing comet races toward Earth. John Garrity (Gerard Butler), his estranged wife Allison (Morena Baccarin), and young son Nathan make a perilous journey to their only hope for sanctuary. Amid terrifying news accounts of cities around the world being leveled by the comet's fragments, the Garritys experience the best and worst in humanity while they battle the increasing panic and lawlessness surrounding them. As the countdown to the global apocalypse approaches zero, their incredible trek culminates in a desperate and last-minute flight to a possible safe haven.

movies.title: A Wife's Nightmare
movies.description: Liz, newly returned home after a mental breakdown, must welcome a relative stranger into her home when Caitlin, a vivacious young woman, claims to be her husband's daughter. As Liz's life begins to unravel, she must determine if Caitlin is the source of her problems or if she is falling back into her old issues.

movies.title: Not Without My Daughter
movies.description: An American woman, trapped in Islamic Iran by her brutish husband, must find a way to escape with her daughter as well. Based on the true story of Betty Mahmoody's harrowing escape from Iran with her daughter.

movies.title: Believe Me: The Abduction of Lisa McVey
movies.description: On the night she plans to take her own life, a 17-year-old girl is kidnapped and finds herself fighting to stay alive. She manages to talk her attacker into releasing her, but when she returns home, no one believes her story except for one detective, who suspects she was abducted by a serial killer. Based on horrifying true events.

movies.title: Back to the Future
movies.description: Marty McFly, a 17-year-old high school student, is accidentally sent 30 years into the past in a time-traveling DeLorean invented by his close friend, the maverick scientist Doc Brown.

movies.title: Back to the Future Part II
movies.description: After visiting 2015, Marty McFly must repeat his visit to 1955 to prevent disastrous changes to 1985...without interfering with his first trip.

movies.title: Back to the Future Part III
movies.description: Stranded in 1955, Marty McFly learns about the death of Doc Brown in 1885 and must travel back in time to save him. With no fuel readily available for the DeLorean, the two must figure how to escape the Old West before Emmett is m...

movies.title: The Matrix
movies.description: When a beautiful stranger leads computer hacker Neo to a forbidding underworld, he discovers the shocking truth--the life he knows is the elaborate deception of an evil cyber-intelligence.

movies.title: The Matrix Reloaded
movies.description: Freedom fighters Neo, Trinity and Morpheus continue to lead the revolt against the Machine Army, unleashing their arsenal of extraordinary skills and weaponry against the systematic forces of repression and exploitation.

movies.title: The Matrix Revolutions
movies.description: The human city of Zion defends itself against the massive invasion of the machines as Neo fights to end the war at another front while also opposing the rogue Agent Smith.

movies.title: The Matrix Resurrections
movies.description: Return to a world of two realities: one, everyday life; the other, what lies behind it. To find out if his reality is a construct, to truly know himself, Mr. Anderson will have to choose to follow the white rabbit once more.

movies.title: Fantastic Four
movies.description: Four astronauts have their lives changed forever, when they end up being hit by a cloud of cosmic radiation. Reed Richards now has the ability to stretch his body like elastic. Sue Storm is now the invisible woman. Johnny Storm becomes the human torch and Ben Grimm becomes the 'Thing', a man made out of rock. But there is one problem. The journey's sponsor, Victor Von Doom has also been affected and with full power, is a dangerous force which needs to be stopped, before it's too late.

movies.title: Fantastic Four: Rise of the Silver Surfer
movies.description: The Fantastic Four learn that they aren't the only super-powered beings in the universe when they square off against the powerful Silver Surfer and the planet-eating Galactus.

movies.title: Fantastic Four
movies.description: Four young outsiders teleport to an alternate and dangerous universe which alters their physical form in shocking ways. The four must learn to harness their new abilities and work together to save Earth from a former friend turned enemy.

movies.title: Den of Thieves
movies.description: A gritty L.A crime saga which follows the intersecting and often personally connected lives of an elite unit of the LA County Sheriff's Dept. and the state's most successful bank robbery crew as the outlaws plan an impossible heist on the Federal Reserve Bank of downtown Los Angeles.

movies.title: The Princess Diaries
movies.description: Mia Thermopolis, a shy American teenager, learns she is heir to the throne of Genovia. With her friends Lilly and Michael Moscovitz in tow, she tries to navigate through the rest of her sixteenth year while being taught how to be a princess by her grandmother, Queen Clarisse Renaldi.

movies.title: The Princess Diaries 2: Royal Engagement
movies.description: Princess Mia Thermopolis has just turned 21 and is supposed to succeed her grandmother as the Queen of Genovia. But an old law states that an unmarried woman can't be made Queen, so Mia is given 30 days to find a husband, while Viscount Mabrey tries to stop her.

movies.title: Taken
movies.description: A retired CIA agent travels across Europe and relies on his old skills to save his estranged daughter, who has been kidnapped while on a trip to Paris.

movies.title: Marley & Me
movies.description: A family learns important life lessons from their adorable, but naughty and neurotic dog Marley, who teaches them about love and loyalty as their family grows.

movies.title: We Bought a Zoo
